column5: Happy belated birthday Paul! I hope you had a good one!

Nice one Paul...time to blow the froth off a root beer or 2!
Happy Bday to ya!! May you have many more!!
Geeze Brian, I hope it was "Happy Birthday"...I'd hate to have to ask my first wife to find out for sure...
Not to worry Beans ole Bud.Its Happy birthday.Mind you, i am english, but dont tell the Qweebekers that or i may lose my job as a Spy for the federals.
Best wishes Paul. I'll be toasting a root beer in your honour today!!  Your good friend, Simon
